214:  * - look for the following string: ------- Forwarded Message -------
215:  *
216:  * REPLY CASE
217:  * - start by checking of the contents contains one line finishing with a colon and includes an email address and a chevron (cheap)
218:  * - look for the following string: On Tuesday, 24 september 2024 at 4:00 PM, Sender <sender@address> wrote: (expensive)
